{"tid":989205,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"練舞跌傷手！韓子亮啪止痛藥拍MV","createTime":"2019-01-20T16:10:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T13:29:58.000Z","uid":136738,"like":9,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6da0ed5e1a07a1053043619112f100e2f460fe25","tid":989205,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"歌手韓子亮（TL）日前為今年頭炮新歌《Baby Wanna Let You Know》拍MV，更邀請了藝人王雯（Nuna）和李海清（JoJo）助陣並擔任女主角。他為求進步，在拍攝新歌MV前，與排舞師日練夜練，最終卻練出個傷來！他說：「有個跳舞動作要踢腳，但當時我失平衡跌倒，一跌隻左手就受傷，個跌打師傅話我係勞損、傷咗韌帶，起碼要成個月先好得番。」可是他卻沒聽跌打師傅叮囑繼續練習，他說：「咁我唔識跳舞，所以只好靠後天努力練習，希望日後會更加進步！」 <br />\n<br />\n他直言要食止痛藥才能拍攝：「都唔可以太細動作，因為呢個MV都大製作，有排舞師、6個Dancers，用兩部機拍，加埋演員成30幾人，我哋走咗幾個景，有中環外景、酒吧、同自己喺觀塘搭咗個景出嚟，所以今次個陣容同製作都幾大，都冇得避忌個傷，要落力啲跳。」 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190120/mobile/bkn-20190120044927818-0120_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190120%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190120044927818-0120_00862_001.html&d=PyfV2BFkE3UcgS07YhdWP8KJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=f5bd745f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190120/mobile/bkn-20190120044927818-0120_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3df6fcbd9bb7da33c85885c6629b152c9aca3a86","tid":989205,"uid":198992,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"TLbb 慘慘豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2953a43ea627b1cd6f66324395a89b8397a5cb44","tid":989205,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vJEko6E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvJEko6E.png&h=7ad34808&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https:/